OL,4,CUK faces tougher austerity era, ex-Bank
OL,5,Cchief warns
OL,6, The UK faces a "more difficult" era of
OL,7, austerity than the one following the
OL,8, financial crisis in order to stabilise
OL,9, the economy, a former governor of the
OL,10, Bank of England has warned.
OL,12,FLord Mervyn King said the average
OL,13,Fperson could face "significantly higher
OL,14,Ftaxes" to fund public spending.
OL,16,FChancellor Jeremy Hunt is scheduled to
OL,17,Fset out his economic plans on 31
OL,18,FOctober.
OL,20,FHe has already scrapped almost all the
OL,21,Ftax cuts announced under Liz Truss.
